&lt;p&gt;The first photography experience is created by a flash idea that I want to do something to fill my boring daily life. Due to the lack of goal to guide my life, I choose the photography. Before I buy a mirrorless camera, I rent an XT30 to experience the difference of mirrorless camera and smartphone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At noon, I got my XT30. But I feel panic. It is so expensive, I&#39;m scare that if I will break it. I didn&#39;t know why I thought the zjx at that moment. Because I&#39;m neverous? Maybe this is a point zjx dislike. Hope I could change this weakness. As a beginner, I invited a great teacher to guide how to take a beautiful photo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We choosed The Shanghai Bund as the destination. We got the Bund at four o&#39;clock at afternoon, I took many photos. As the works of first time, I think these photo is great.&lt;/p&gt;
